# Project 2 – Backend API Development
**DecodeLabs Industrial Training Kit | Full Stack Development Internship**

## 📌 Overview
This is Project 2 of the DecodeLabs Industrial Training Kit — the "integration phase" of the
internship. The goal was to build a simple, reliable backend API that handles application
logic: creating, reading, updating, and validating data through clean REST endpoints.

The deliverable is the **Drafting Board API**, a RESTful task-management API built with
Node.js and Express, designed as the backend companion to the Project 1 frontend.

## 🎯 Project Goal
Develop a simple backend API to handle application logic, including:
- API endpoints (GET / POST, plus PUT / DELETE)
- Handling of user input and responses
- Basic data validation

## 🛠️ Built With
- **Node.js**
- **Express.js**
- In-memory data store (no external database required)

