## 🔌 API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint            | Description                          | Success Code |
|--------|---------------------|---------------------------------------|---------------|
| GET    | `/`                  | Health check + endpoint list          | 200 |
| GET    | `/api/tasks`         | List all tasks                        | 200 |
| GET    | `/api/tasks?done=true` | Filter tasks by completion status  | 200 |
| GET    | `/api/tasks/:id`     | Get a single task                     | 200 |
| POST   | `/api/tasks`         | Create a new task                     | 201 |
| PUT    | `/api/tasks/:id`     | Update an existing task                | 200 |
| DELETE | `/api/tasks/:id`     | Remove a task                         | 204 |

## 🧾 Status Codes Used
- `200 OK`, `201 Created`, `204 No Content`
- `400 Bad Request` – failed validation
- `404 Not Found` – unknown route or task id
- `500 Internal Server Error` – unexpected failure

